T02TD1956E:83b-1: krishna ya m'a ri sh'anti ho ma bi dhi n'a ma /
T02TD1956E:83b-3: gshin rje gshed nag po'i zhi ba'i sbyin sreg gi cho ga zhes bya ba /
T02TD1956E:83b-4: mgon po 'jam dpal la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1956E:83b-5: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid can //
T02TD1956E:83b-6: char sprin gzhon nu'i mdog 'dra ba //
T02TD1956E:83b-7: rtog bral lhun gyis skyes pa'i bdag / gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal te //
T02TD1956E:83b-8: sdig pa zhi dang bsod nams 'phel //
T02TD1956E:83b-9: dbang du bya dang tshar bcad dang //
T02TD1956E:83b-10: dngos grub myur du thob bya'i phyir //
T02TD1956E:83b-11: bdag gis sbyin sreg bshad par bya //
T02TD1956E:83b-12: bde gshegs chos kyi sku dag gi //
T02TD1956E:83b-13: bsnyen pa sngon du song ba yis //
T02TD1956E:83b-14: yid dga' ba yis phyogs su //
T02TD1956E:83b-15: bkra shis bzang po'i gzhi dag la //
T02TD1956E:83b-16: mtshan nyid ldan pa'i sa sbyangs nas //
T02TD1956E:83b-17: tshad dang ldan pa'i thab khung ni //
T02TD1956E:83b-18: rgyar ni khru gang zabs su phyed //
T02TD1956E:83b-19: kha khyer sor bzhi dor nas kyang //
T02TD1956E:83b-20: dpangs dang rgya ru sor bzhi brtsig //
T02TD1956E:83b-21: phyogs kyi thad kar sor gnyis las //
T02TD1956E:83b-22: dra ba zla tshe rdo rje'i gzugs //
T02TD1956E:83b-23: kha dog dkar po nyid byas te //
T02TD1956E:84a-0: @84a * // me tog dkar po dus gsum gtor //
T02TD1956E:84a-1: nang du 'dab brgyad dkar po bri //
T02TD1956E:84a-2: 'khor lo rdo rje rin chen dang //
T02TD1956E:84a-3: padma ral gri phyag rgya dgod //
T02TD1956E:84a-4: nang du rdo rje'i phreng ba ste //
T02TD1956E:84a-5: kha khyer me ris rnam par bskor //
T02TD1956E:84a-6: thab kyi dbang du byas pa'o //
T02TD1956E:84a-7: bud shing tshad ni khru gang la //
T02TD1956E:84a-8: skam pa dang ni rnying pa dag / rul dang srog chags rnam spangs te //
T02TD1956E:84a-9: n+ya gro dha dang p'a la sha / sha mi ta dang dri bzangs dang //
T02TD1956E:84a-10: byang chub shing dang tsandan dang //
T02TD1956E:84a-11: dri zhim bzang po'i shing de dag / thab kyi khor khor yug tu //
T02TD1956E:84a-12: ku sha sngon po bkram pa'i steng //
T02TD1956E:84a-13: thab khung dma' bar legs brtsigs la //
T02TD1956E:84a-14: sbrang rtsi 'o ma dri chus byug / bud shing dbang du byas pa'o //
T02TD1956E:84a-16: shing ngam dri zhim shing dag la //
T02TD1956E:84a-17: rtse mo'i cha las byung ba yi //
T02TD1956E:84a-18: rlon dang 'dab mar bcas pa ste //
T02TD1956E:84a-19: sor bcu'i tshad du mngon par gsungs //
T02TD1956E:84a-20: dri chu 'o mas sbags la bzhag / rtse gnyis gas dang chag pa dang //
T02TD1956E:84a-21: 'bus zos pa dang srog chags bcas //
T02TD1956E:84a-22: shun pa med dang brla bskams dang //
T02TD1956E:84a-23: yo dang rul dang sbom pa dang //
T02TD1956E:84a-24: ring thung phra ba rnam par spangs //
T02TD1956E:84a-25: gdags yig btags la bsreg par bya //
T02TD1956E:84a-26: bye brag dang ni sde tshan no //
T02TD1956E:84a-27: na ma: sh'anti dku ru sv'a h'a /
T02TD1956E:84a-28: au ma ka sye sarba tre ha nam /
T02TD1956E:84a-34: sarba aa mam ga le nam /
T02TD1956E:84a-35: sarba du ra ni mi ta nam /
T02TD1956E:84a-36: sarba p'a pam karm'a ba ra nam /
T02TD1956E:84a-38: til dang yungs kar rgyal po ni //
T02TD1956E:84a-39: sdig pa sbyang phyir bsreg par bya //
T02TD1956E:84a-40: aom sarba p'a pam da ha na badzr'a ya h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1956E:84a-41: de nas mchod bstod gsol ba gdab //
T02TD1956E:84a-42: dgang blugs phul la bsreg par bya //
T02TD1956E:84a-43: ye shes gshegs la dam tshig bsdu //
T02TD1956E:84a-45: de nas me sbyangs sreg rdzas kyi //
T02TD1956E:84a-46: lhag ma ji snyed pa rnams ni //
T02TD1956E:84a-47: me yi lha la sngags kyis dbul //
T02TD1956E:84a-48: mchod bstod dgang blugs bzod gsol bya //
T02TD1956E:84a-49: ye shes me lha gshegs su gsol //
T02TD1956E:84a-50: dam tshig 'bar ba'i rnam par bstim //
T02TD1956E:84a-51: de nas bdag gi phyag rgya che //
T02TD1956E:84b-0: dgrol dang thugs kar bsdu tshul @84b gyis //
T02TD1956E:84b-1: dam tshig rgyal por gnas nas kyang //
T02TD1956E:84b-2: thab la bskor zhing me tog dbul //
T02TD1956E:84b-3: de nas glegs bam klog la sogs //
T02TD1956E:84b-4: ji ltar mthun pa'i spyod lam bya //
T02TD1956E:84b-5: sgrub thabs mngon rtogs 'di dag ni //
T02TD1956E:84b-6: dngos grub thob phyir bdag gis brtsams //
T02TD1956E:84b-7: 'di yis bsod nams gang thob des //
T02TD1956E:84b-8: kun gyi thun mong mchog thob shog / dpal gshin rje gshed nag po'i zhi ba'i sbyin sreg gi cho ga rdzogs so /
T02TD1956E:84b-10: // / bla ma nag po'i zhabs nyid chen po la //
T02TD1956E:84b-11: gser gling rnal 'byor gu na dzny'a na yis //
T02TD1956E:84b-12: bram ze karma tsandra btang nas kyang //
T02TD1956E:84b-13: rnal 'byor rnams kyi zhal ngor sbyin sreg 'di //
T02TD1956E:84b-14: dpal mchog rdo rje gdan du rnam par brtsams //
T02TD1956E:84b-15: theg pa che la nyi ma'i 'od bzhin mdzes //
T02TD1956E:84b-16: rnal 'byor pa bsod nams pa pra dzny'a shr'i dzny'a na k'i rtis rang 'gyur du byas pa'o//
